txt.en: Charged by the masters of Gramsfoot you are told to go to Hoarhallow and kill the Hobbits there for a feast. Goblins from Grothum will come along and scoop up the bodies that you leave behind.
'Killed them good you did. We'll gather 'em up and bring them to Uglash. I'll have the boys clear a path for you back to Gramsfoot.'
